{"tid":1758494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2011年]黃毓民：泛民支持修改議事規則打開了缺口，將來必陸續有來！","createTime":"2019-11-27T05:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T14:46:51.000Z","uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0d37691aac88395199a5834780539eaa10d76cbb","tid":1758494,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkk39dBGPAt4&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=52e740af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4</a><br />\n教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來呢段片已經8年"},{"pid":"02a96504a2d69fb83e4ca29b7a4e658549b30666","tid":1758494,"uid":198590,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 共同分享(C506)</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>不如幫幫白鴿黨裝修 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>11年同15年屌人民力量同熱血公民票<br />\n今日就鳩沙田友既票<br />\n咁就送左席比民賤聯<br />\n道歉Sorry好撚假囉<br />\n人地議席就無左咩都無<br />\n你地今次就大勝食咁多議席<br />\n仲要好多區比你地逼到退選讓路含淚投<br />\n<br />\n既然你地食人血饅頭食得咁開心<br />\n手足陣間不如發夢去是旦一個白鴿黨既辦事署裝下修<br />\n反正你地今次賺咁多經費咁多人工<br />\n比2條路你地揀<br />\n裝修/捐一半人工做抗爭基金<br />\n就係咁</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1753849/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>新口號同洗腦金句！想贏既入嚟同我宣傳出去 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>將香港人 反抗<br />\n變做<br />\n香港人 返工<br />\n成個口號幾撚震撼</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1692157/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>保護休班警,你我有責 - #4</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔好搞休班警<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1692143/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實借運動識女溝女有咩問題 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>CCtai班友仔做咩咁敏感<br />\n大家都係有相同興趣同諗法<br />\n傾得埋再交換contact上埋床有咩問題<br />\nCCTai班小朋友真係大驚小怪</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1669147/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>其實借運動食女真係無問題 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>你情我願<br />\n有咩好屌<br />\n得班前線葡萄撚會屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 抄左幾十個絲打電話IG 食過幾個<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Ftongue.gif&h=94eb9256&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Ftongue.gif&h=94eb9256&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1669122/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1669122/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"c0eae7d9d936f762b1abdbc849e762e792a23ddf","tid":1758494,"uid":67232,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:53:17.000Z","msg":"樓主收到錢未"},{"pid":"b22874648bad8cb454fda1efdec4352bc8d1965a","tid":1758494,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"泛民當年屌本土係同今日屌白票一樣，完全唔理解人地論述，先將佢打成票係鬼係敵人先，跟住叫選民繼續含撚，我希望呢半年真係令泛民醒覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[警世]睇泛民評論似乎佢地仲未理解&ldquo;含撚投票&rdquo;本身有咩問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756863</a>"},{"pid":"f8483b20fe89bc1753a08f236875f24e588b9cd9","tid":1758494,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b22874648bad8cb454fda1efdec4352bc8d1965a","tid":1758494,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"泛民當年屌本土係同今日屌白票一樣，完全唔理解人地論述，先將佢打成票係鬼係敵人先，跟住叫選民繼續含撚，我希望呢半年真係令泛民醒覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[警世]睇泛民評論似乎佢地仲未理解&ldquo;含撚投票&rdquo;本身有咩問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756863</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T05:57:37.000Z","msg":"ching竟然無比人屌<br />\n介唔介意我之後copy你段野開post睇d&ldquo;鬼&rdquo;點回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937017c61ccb183c1ba9b845c7468e185b6263ab","tid":1758494,"uid":266755,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"黃毓民一生人花咗超過10年屌泛民。"},{"pid":"f58ed35f0c6121dc42666cafab50efc16cd04054","tid":1758494,"uid":8562,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"8年啦<br />\n仲拎出黎講<br />\n飯民係錯架啦, 仲做錯唔少野<br />\n樓豬低質分化撚"},{"pid":"88c1